---
summary: Disable user signup in the default config
---
assignee: erikj
created: 2015-03-13 13:08:46.0
creator: matthew
description: |-
  It can be an unpleasant surprise for folks running homeservers to discover they have public signup turned on.

  We should disable it by default, and provide a script & instructions for manually creating accounts.  If the user enables it, we should encourage them to set up a captcha too.
